    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Amy, re: freezing the dough, absolutely.  By all means!  I can&#39;t say how long it will keep, though, because it depends on your freezer.  There&#39;s no real reason for it to go bad &#8211; the freezer prevents spoilage &#8211; but after a while, I do find that things start to get freezer burn, or they smell and taste like the freezer&#8230;</p>
