  <li id="comment-35843" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/07568818488450292422" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">les and joe</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2012/01/you-can-count-on-me/#comment-35843"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2012-01-17T23:01:36-05:00">Tuesday, January 17, 2012 at 11:01 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Check out Dorie Greenspan&#39;s recipe for World Peace cookies if you are looking for a more shortbread-y but still super chocolatey cookie. The amount of chocolate in here is more though so these may take the chocolate cake.</p>
    </div>

      </li><!-- #comment-## -->
