    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I made a whole-wheat version of these (the dough was strange &#8211; almost mousse-like and impossibley messy to roll and/or drop [I tried both], not that this is something to complain about, because it&#39;s delicious from fingers, too), as well as a really beautiful burnt caramel sauce (a la Recchiuti, but without having to pay for shipping) and homemade whipped cream. They. Were. Amazing.</p>
<p>(Note the &#8220;were&#8221; there &#8211; one night, all gone. Ridiculous.)</p>
<p>Anyhow, as ever &#8211; thanks!</p>
